{"tid":609452,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請參加【 死諫烈士熊家俊 - 百日悼念會 】","createTime":"2018-03-29T05:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T13:05:38.000Z","uid":28366,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5ee5da8ece7e77c0db4bc985358575c74a196b6c","tid":609452,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/29060489_1902007489844390_5922954333208876803_o.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=eaa4ada5657da43eb4f24df58df09e37&amp;oe=5B6F7343\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2F29060489_1902007489844390_5922954333208876803_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3Deaa4ada5657da43eb4f24df58df09e37%26oe%3D5B6F7343&h=37c0cf2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【百日追悼晚會 死諫烈士 - 熊家俊】<br />\n<br />\n遺言：「唔好信一地兩檢無跨境執法」<br />\n<br />\n2018年一地兩檢強行通車，危機在即，2017年12月15日浸大學生熊家俊從浸大校園5樓躍下，犧牲生命以死相諫，提醒香港人不要相信一地兩檢，沒有跨境擄人！<br />\n<br />\n為了紀念熊家俊烈士，並警醒港人，我們於家俊逝世105天舉行「百日悼念晚會」。<br />\n<br />\n詳情：<br />\n<br />\n日期：<span style=\"color: red;\">2018年 3月29日(星期四)</span><br />\n時間：6:00pm <br />\n地點：浸會大學道校園教學及行政大樓3樓平台<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171216/20246426\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F20246426&d=m0IYAp8BOsm1xMdwEBNi%2FzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b4007dd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171216%2F20246426&h=a2c89eea\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171216/20246426</a>"},{"pid":"809ef2ab24f712296eb202ec643ba03eb180e020","tid":609452,"uid":28366,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:18:08.000Z","msg":"悼念會後《學生獨立聯盟 》有新加入成員簡介會，歡迎參加。<br />\n<br />\n申請表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/Oi0MbJs9oZsSYFTl2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FOi0MbJs9oZsSYFTl2&d=m0IYAp8BOsm1xMdwEBNi%2FzQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=0d2b48af\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/Oi0MbJs9oZsSYFTl2</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">P.S 而家開始八大院校都有人加入，asso 同 ive 都唔少人<br />\n<br />\n傾好就會搞啲有影響力嘅行動</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ca70fe7822538bd7a4ff2611131ed3bcd243f52","tid":609452,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"今晚見"},{"pid":"273f14e4d808adb4e7d0660d3be21b04f9566112","tid":609452,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0ca70fe7822538bd7a4ff2611131ed3bcd243f52","tid":609452,"uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:18:24.000Z","msg":"今晚見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:20:00.000Z","msg":"去"},{"pid":"d4ef16d0a3f6e63bc472b9e2e63593b13c9e7e73","tid":609452,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:21:40.000Z","msg":"去"},{"pid":"c2a9b1562b9b6fcce5db527317bc3cb227a7c589","tid":609452,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:22:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d54e3c029c87cd821a5eb540538018c16f7ce594","tid":609452,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0853ddf4a2a4ebb16c54a476381d8119da99b32","tid":609452,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:23:19.000Z","msg":"去"},{"pid":"755b5c4d43effab091164de17214b6e371764370","tid":609452,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:28:22.000Z","msg":"去"},{"pid":"9c95a08b01bfbcdaad05a0ca4865242a01ca7ac2","tid":609452,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:29:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e069175250ce6fc46456c3cb708533f0c151277e","tid":609452,"uid":116054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T05:46